    "description": "<p>Eric Ong &amp; Associates Pte Ltd was established by Mr Eric Ong in June 2019, who is striving for Facilities &amp; Property Management more than 25 years as Management Agent. It is not only managing Residential buildings but also mix Commercial buildings in Singapore. We have a professional and effective standard procedures such as Estate &amp; Facilities management, property upgrading consultancy service, financial &amp; accounting support, Human Resource &amp; staff promotion management, advertising and staff upgrading program etc.</p>\n<p>Our people is our key asset. We emphasize our staff’s working skills, professional knowledge, personal &amp; employment development, the priority opportunity in promotion and upgrading program. We are welcome all of you from various backgrounds, age and ethnic groups, come from all across the region. &nbsp;Together with our goals and enterprise spirits to value, expertise and responsible into our excellent performance to our clients.</p>",
